{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac@2.pkg/1772602400196/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602400552", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac@2.pkg/1772602400196/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602400552"}, "identifier": "2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗五、六句&ldquo;昔日长城战，咸言意气高&rdquo;，这不是昔日战斗场景，而是众人的说法。诗人没有从正面进行辨别或评论，而是用&ldquo;黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿&rdquo;来回答。意思是战死者的白骨，杂乱地弃在蓬蒿间，从古到今，都是如此。这首诗着重表现战争的残酷以及诗人对战争的厌恶。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​雁门太守行</span>​</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李贺</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​​塞下曲</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>王昌龄</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>饮马渡秋水，水寒风似刀。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>平沙日未没，黯黯见临洮。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>昔日长城战，咸言意气高。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】雁门太守行唐 .李贺黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。 【乙】塞下曲唐 .王昌龄饮马渡秋水，水寒风似刀。平沙日未没，黯黯见临洮。昔日长城战，咸言意气高。黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac@2.pkg/item.json?v=1751871821746", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】诗擅用色彩写意境。&ldquo;黑&rdquo;与&ldquo;金&rdquo;相映，烘托出大战在即的凝重。&ldquo;燕脂&rdquo;与&ldquo;紫&rdquo;的浓艳，绘出了战斗的惨烈。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗中&ldquo;风似刀&rdquo;运用比喻的修辞手法，生动形象地展现了塞外秋风的猛烈与寒冷。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两诗的五、六句都追忆了昔日战斗场景，侧面烘托出战斗的艰苦和战士们的英勇善战。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗的结尾都抒发了情感。【甲】诗借用典故抒发官兵们忘身报国之情；【乙】诗以&ldquo;乱&rdquo;字将对牺牲将士的哀悼蕴含其中。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​雁门太守行</span>​</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李贺</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​​塞下曲</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>王昌龄</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>饮马渡秋水，水寒风似刀。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>平沙日未没，黯黯见临洮。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>昔日长城战，咸言意气高。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】雁门太守行唐 .李贺黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。 【乙】塞下曲唐 .王昌龄饮马渡秋水，水寒风似刀。平沙日未没，黯黯见临洮。昔日长城战，咸言意气高。黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿。"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​雁门太守行</span>​</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李贺</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黑云压城城欲摧，甲光向日金鳞开。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>角声满天秋色里，塞上燕脂凝夜紫。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>半卷红旗临易水，霜重鼓寒声不起。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>报君黄金台上意，提携玉龙为君死。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​​塞下曲</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>王昌龄</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>饮马渡秋水，水寒风似刀。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>平沙日未没，黯黯见临洮。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>昔日长城战，咸言意气高。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>黄尘足今古，白骨乱蓬蒿。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac@2.pkg/1772602400196/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602400552", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac@2.pkg/1772602400196/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602400552"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2024", "nature": "tm_sync", "audit_teacher_ids": ["df813dcb-9b5d-4ee9-a018-e8823c375371"], "version_source_id": "2ca47161-fbf8-43b6-96ed-867b74574eac", "format": "2d641585-d91b-4d65-8f5a-2a7fd8103ac7", "faculty_advisor_ids": ["0d011f6a-8dcb-4adb-8f5b-13c5783254be"], "producer_ids": [], "teacher_ids": ["2930916d-a2a0-493c-b927-4cff25172888"], "audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "sys_resource_space": 159739, "thumbnail_audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "qb_qu_num": 4, "res_sort": 202507071444504, "size": 836578, "produce_type": "artificiality", "thu